	Rarity Normal Magic Rare
	BaseType == "Dusk Amulet" "Dusk Ring" "Gloam Amulet" "Gloam Ring" "Penumbra Amulet" "Penumbra Ring" "Tenebrous Amulet" "Tenebrous Ring"
